        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>STOP Act 2.0</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Government Accountability Office to evaluate the implementation of a 2018 law that requires increased shipment-tracking responsibilities and coordination between the U.S. Postal Service and U.S. Customs and Border Protection regarding international shipments of controlled substances (e.g., fentanyl).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
